				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10797539/scp-4235#post-4197034</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2019 02:38:57 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Jakuwoski</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3382837</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Those are only side effects associated with the object, not the effect it seeks. There are also other MC&amp;D products with harmful effects associated with inappropriate use, such as Kaiju caviar or unicorn horn extract, and even products focused on causing harm.</p> <p>These are just roses that don't wither for a certain price&#8230;</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
